WEBVTT

01:26.520 --> 01:35.020
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.490 --> 01:37.940
[Episode 28]

01:42.259 --> 01:43.190
Take this money.

01:43.870 --> 01:44.930
If I don't finish the task,

01:44.930 --> 01:46.530
Shengli won't let me go back.

01:47.140 --> 01:48.100
Thank him for me.

01:48.280 --> 01:49.009
Thank him yourself.

01:49.009 --> 01:50.610
Stop using me as a messenger.

01:50.650 --> 01:51.810
He's been very tired lately,

01:51.810 --> 01:54.670
traveling back and forth
between Russia and China.

01:55.140 --> 01:56.200
How is your mother?

01:56.780 --> 01:57.509
Much better.

01:57.539 --> 01:58.570
That's good.

01:58.570 --> 02:00.030
Heaven protects the good.

02:00.180 --> 02:00.950
How are you guys doing?

02:00.950 --> 02:02.410
Is everything going well?

02:02.850 --> 02:04.090
With Mr. Lucky around,

02:04.090 --> 02:06.330
any accident will turn out fine.

02:07.760 --> 02:09.030
Did something happen?

02:10.900 --> 02:11.400
See?

02:11.900 --> 02:13.030
I told you any accident
would turn out fine.

02:13.030 --> 02:14.430
Why are you still asking?

02:14.430 --> 02:15.580
You are worried about him, aren't you?

02:15.580 --> 02:16.230
It's fine. It's fine.

02:16.230 --> 02:17.329
Everything's great.

02:17.329 --> 02:18.210
Don't just sit there.

02:18.210 --> 02:19.470
Have a bowl of noodles.

02:19.620 --> 02:20.750
I've already eaten.

02:26.240 --> 02:26.930
It looks like

02:26.930 --> 02:28.730
you guys have made quite a scene.

02:29.079 --> 02:31.210
Does he still have time for that movie?

02:36.180 --> 02:37.180
Wh-What's wrong?

02:38.250 --> 02:39.650
I knew he didn't tell you.

02:42.130 --> 02:43.660
Is the movie not going well?

02:43.910 --> 02:45.090
Ask him yourself.

02:45.180 --> 02:46.020
If I tell you,

02:46.040 --> 02:46.640
I'll...

02:46.780 --> 02:48.360
I'll be gossiping again.

02:52.860 --> 02:53.770
But if I tell you,

02:53.770 --> 02:55.170
don't say I told you that.

02:55.750 --> 02:57.000
It's not about
whether it's going well or not.

02:57.000 --> 02:58.650
That movie fell through long ago.

02:58.650 --> 02:59.940
When did this happen?

03:00.060 --> 03:01.430
Right at the start of autumn.

03:01.430 --> 03:02.430
Were you two

03:03.590 --> 03:05.090
having a little fight

03:05.090 --> 03:06.690
and not contacting each other
or something?

03:06.690 --> 03:08.460
And his movie at that time...

03:08.520 --> 03:09.140
didn't...

03:09.340 --> 03:10.650
didn't get its investment back.

03:10.650 --> 03:11.470
Not only did he owe favors,

03:11.470 --> 03:12.930
he also got into deep debt.

03:14.090 --> 03:14.960
He's in debt?

03:15.000 --> 03:16.130
How much does he owe?

03:16.370 --> 03:17.090
That... that...

03:17.090 --> 03:18.090
That's nothing you need to worry about.

03:18.090 --> 03:19.360
Once we close this deal,

03:19.360 --> 03:20.420
he'll cover the deficit.

03:20.420 --> 03:21.150
It's fine.

03:23.250 --> 03:24.100
I told him

03:24.400 --> 03:25.900
that the movie industry is tough.

03:25.900 --> 03:26.960
The audience nowadays

03:26.960 --> 03:27.650
is less and less willing to

03:27.650 --> 03:28.560
go to the cinema.

03:28.560 --> 03:30.650
Everyone watches TV series at home, right?

03:30.650 --> 03:31.210
But look,

03:33.079 --> 03:34.530
you actually like Shengli quite a bit.

03:34.530 --> 03:36.390
And Shengli likes you too, right?

03:36.520 --> 03:37.320
I feel like...

03:37.840 --> 03:38.800
maybe you two

03:38.820 --> 03:40.420
think of each other too much.

03:40.650 --> 03:41.710
Communicate more,

03:41.800 --> 03:43.800
keep in touch, and make phone calls.

03:44.410 --> 03:46.190
Any difficulty will pass.

03:46.400 --> 03:47.010
Right?

03:47.460 --> 03:49.280
Let me tell you something honestly.

03:49.280 --> 03:51.490
Even if fate is full of hardships,

03:52.240 --> 03:54.650
even if it takes strange
and winding turns,

03:55.030 --> 03:56.840
don't cry, don't feel bitter.

03:57.590 --> 03:58.360
Shengli

03:58.630 --> 04:00.690
will definitely be with you forever.

04:04.310 --> 04:04.880
Right?

04:09.920 --> 04:11.000
Sir, the chili here

04:11.000 --> 04:11.990
is a bit too spicy.

04:11.990 --> 04:12.990
Do you have water?

04:13.310 --> 04:14.310
Do you have water?

04:14.400 --> 04:15.010
Yes, we do.

04:15.520 --> 04:16.370
But that's boiling water.

04:16.370 --> 04:17.630
Boiling water is fine.

04:21.170 --> 04:23.850
[Seasons Change Hostel]

04:22.360 --> 04:22.920
Dad.

04:23.000 --> 04:23.450
What?

04:23.510 --> 04:25.870
Are you really going back
to our hometown with me?

04:25.870 --> 04:27.130
How long will you stay?

04:27.420 --> 04:28.830
What do you mean by that?

04:29.240 --> 04:30.250
That's my home.

04:30.370 --> 04:32.170
How long do you think I'll stay?

04:32.720 --> 04:33.670
Geez.

04:33.720 --> 04:35.190
Does that mean you will stay with me

04:35.190 --> 04:36.520
and Mom every day?

04:36.810 --> 04:37.830
Of course.

04:39.040 --> 04:41.060
All these years in Beijing,

04:41.130 --> 04:43.420
I've just been making money
for your mom's treatment.

04:43.420 --> 04:46.360
Now that she's cured,
we can reunite at home.

04:47.180 --> 04:48.590
We have to work together

04:48.620 --> 04:50.280
to teach your mom how to speak.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.100
I know.

04:51.540 --> 04:53.250
The way I learned to speak
when I was little

04:53.250 --> 04:54.450
is how I'll teach Mom.

04:54.680 --> 04:55.710
That's right.

04:56.040 --> 04:58.390
You're a big boy now.

04:58.420 --> 04:58.900
Right?

04:59.060 --> 05:00.900
You should teach your mom

05:00.930 --> 05:02.030
to speak the way

05:02.060 --> 05:03.190
you'd teach a child.

05:11.430 --> 05:11.920
Right.

05:11.930 --> 05:14.380
When the three of us are together,

05:14.800 --> 05:15.830
we can be at ease.

05:16.250 --> 05:18.300
Try to speak as much as you can.

05:18.360 --> 05:19.630
Don't use gestures.

05:19.660 --> 05:21.610
You have to practice speaking.

05:21.640 --> 05:23.170
Practice speaking. Speak.

05:23.720 --> 05:25.720
You have to be brave enough to speak.

05:25.860 --> 05:27.130
Speak. Don't gesture.

05:27.300 --> 05:27.770
Speak.

05:32.720 --> 05:33.580
Don't gesture.

05:33.630 --> 05:34.370
Understood.

05:34.430 --> 05:35.750
Understood. Understood.

05:35.750 --> 05:37.520
We can be at ease.

05:37.600 --> 05:39.159
We can be at ease now.

05:39.370 --> 05:39.860
Right.

05:40.220 --> 05:40.920
When are we going

05:40.920 --> 05:42.200
to see Ranran?

05:42.240 --> 05:43.210
When?

05:43.890 --> 05:44.680
Let's set...

05:45.740 --> 05:46.390
Ranran?

05:47.310 --> 05:47.860
Ranran.

05:47.950 --> 05:49.740
Why did you come back alone?

05:49.920 --> 05:51.120
Where's Liangliang?

05:51.659 --> 05:53.790
Liangliang went to buy train tickets.

05:53.870 --> 05:55.400
We need to go back to Huzhou.

06:00.680 --> 06:01.330
Ranran,

06:01.480 --> 06:02.410
my mom is asking,

06:02.450 --> 06:03.610
"Why are you back?

06:03.930 --> 06:05.060
How's your health?"

06:06.600 --> 06:08.410
I'm fine. I'm fine.

06:09.300 --> 06:10.360
Liangliang told me

06:10.740 --> 06:11.570
that you guys

06:12.350 --> 06:14.720
are going back to your hometown
in the next couple of days.

06:14.720 --> 06:16.320
I want to say goodbye to you.

06:16.570 --> 06:17.860
We're not in a rush.

06:17.880 --> 06:20.010
We're leaving the day after tomorrow.

06:20.750 --> 06:22.680
After you go back to your hometown,

06:23.220 --> 06:24.250
if there are any difficulties,

06:24.250 --> 06:24.910
you must...

06:25.010 --> 06:25.680
you must...

06:25.700 --> 06:26.880
call me.

06:27.000 --> 06:27.510
Okay.

06:29.070 --> 06:30.250
Xiaobao, you too.

06:30.250 --> 06:31.150
You must study hard.

06:31.150 --> 06:32.550
You must learn more words

06:32.800 --> 06:33.659
and write to me.

06:34.250 --> 06:35.920
Don't worry, Ranran.

06:36.360 --> 06:37.790
When my mother can speak,

06:37.890 --> 06:39.200
she will call you.

06:41.930 --> 06:42.909
Will it be...

06:43.890 --> 06:44.520
hard to

06:44.550 --> 06:46.080
see you again in the future?

06:46.420 --> 06:47.770
It's fine, Ranran.

06:48.220 --> 06:49.370
I... I...

06:49.370 --> 06:51.240
am going back to my hometown

06:51.260 --> 06:53.120
to work on making corn juice.

06:53.190 --> 06:54.580
The village will even pay

06:54.580 --> 06:56.650
for me to come to Beijing

06:56.740 --> 06:58.390
to develop the market and study.

06:58.390 --> 06:59.340
When I come to Beijing again,

06:59.340 --> 07:01.670
I'll still stay at Seasons Change Hostel.

07:01.770 --> 07:03.340
I'll still stay in Room 108.

07:03.680 --> 07:04.530
Don't worry.

07:04.740 --> 07:06.270
We'll see each other often.

07:08.130 --> 07:08.990
Ranran,

07:09.430 --> 07:10.870
after I go back to my hometown,

07:10.870 --> 07:12.390
I won't be farming anymore.

07:12.390 --> 07:14.000
But in my heart,

07:14.450 --> 07:16.170
there is a new seed planted.

07:16.690 --> 07:18.490
Although leaving Beijing means

07:18.570 --> 07:20.270
fewer opportunities,

07:21.120 --> 07:21.870
this seed in my heart

07:21.870 --> 07:23.590
can grow into crops

07:23.800 --> 07:24.770
in my hometown

07:25.180 --> 07:26.530
and bring

07:26.810 --> 07:28.730
a new harvest.

07:29.740 --> 07:31.860
Be just like me,

07:32.110 --> 07:32.720
alright?

07:35.560 --> 07:36.180
Mr. Guo,

07:36.560 --> 07:37.120
Mrs. Guo.

07:38.630 --> 07:41.530
The next time you see me,

07:41.770 --> 07:43.090
I'll be a new Ranran.

07:43.570 --> 07:44.100
Alright.

07:54.040 --> 07:55.060
Ranran,

07:55.310 --> 07:56.340
my mom said

07:56.830 --> 07:58.580
we would start over together.

07:59.360 --> 08:00.810
As long as we have each other,

08:00.810 --> 08:02.600
tomorrow will be better.

08:05.620 --> 08:06.540
Ranran,

08:07.100 --> 08:08.500
you are our family.

08:13.310 --> 08:14.620
It's fine, Ranran.

08:15.560 --> 08:18.610
We are family.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.470
Meiqin,

08:30.080 --> 08:32.080
this is what they call a turn of luck.

08:32.720 --> 08:34.340
The shop hasn't been transferred yet,

08:34.340 --> 08:35.840
and you've already been discharged.

08:35.840 --> 08:36.640
Are you happy?

08:37.480 --> 08:38.010
Yes.

08:39.080 --> 08:39.650
I am

08:40.440 --> 08:41.720
just like this shop,

08:42.360 --> 08:43.490
coming back to life.

08:44.290 --> 08:45.670
Why the rush?

08:45.770 --> 08:47.470
You just got discharged.

08:48.370 --> 08:50.170
I really can't stay idle at home.

08:50.510 --> 08:52.310
The customers are all regulars,

08:52.320 --> 08:53.550
so they don't rush me.

08:54.500 --> 08:55.340
Don't worry.

08:56.170 --> 08:58.170
I'll take it depending on my health.

09:01.370 --> 09:02.460
Then I'll

09:02.960 --> 09:04.600
help my mom.

09:05.530 --> 09:06.410
No.

09:06.720 --> 09:08.430
No one can take my shop from me,

09:09.000 --> 09:10.400
not even my own daughter.

09:10.410 --> 09:12.000
Just hurry back to Beijing.

09:17.770 --> 09:19.150
These days,

09:19.550 --> 09:21.250
Shengli has helped us a lot.

09:22.290 --> 09:24.000
It's not easy for him to work hard

09:24.000 --> 09:24.930
alone out there.

09:26.010 --> 09:27.600
And he doesn't have much money.

09:27.600 --> 09:28.500
We need to

09:29.080 --> 09:30.480
return this money to him.

09:31.670 --> 09:33.400
Where did this money come from?

09:33.550 --> 09:34.700
Mr. Yang's factory

09:34.720 --> 09:36.010
is doing very well now.

09:36.270 --> 09:36.980
This is my

09:37.010 --> 09:38.630
agreed dividend.

09:41.770 --> 09:43.470
I can't take this money.

09:43.650 --> 09:45.050
I will pay it back myself.

09:45.130 --> 09:46.360
Listen to me.

09:46.960 --> 09:48.130
I'm not asking about

09:48.170 --> 09:50.570
your relationship with Shengli right now.

09:51.200 --> 09:52.070
But

09:52.870 --> 09:53.790
if you're going to

09:53.790 --> 09:55.160
keep things separate,

09:55.370 --> 09:57.430
return the money to him immediately.

10:01.200 --> 10:03.400
If you're going to share everything...

10:04.410 --> 10:06.010
Then the money belongs to me.

10:06.030 --> 10:08.130
The money still has to go to Shengli.

10:08.460 --> 10:10.280
Do something together.

10:10.770 --> 10:12.510
As long as you have thought it through,

10:12.510 --> 10:13.430
just go for it.

10:13.870 --> 10:14.770
Your mom and I

10:15.010 --> 10:16.840
will always support you.

10:18.170 --> 10:19.320
The saying
"A friend in need is a friend indeed"

10:19.320 --> 10:20.920
applies not just to friends,

10:21.670 --> 10:22.930
but to couples as well.

10:23.860 --> 10:26.090
Meeting someone who never leaves you

10:26.370 --> 10:28.100
and loves you wholeheartedly—

10:28.170 --> 10:29.460
that's a blessing,

10:29.790 --> 10:30.790
and luck.

10:31.890 --> 10:33.200
You should cherish it.

10:35.870 --> 10:36.510
Got it.

10:44.320 --> 10:45.480
Are you going to pay up or not?

10:45.480 --> 10:47.280
I don't have money. How can I pay?

10:55.010 --> 10:55.940
Stop beating me!

10:58.050 --> 10:59.770
Look at this!
This Chinese guy sold us fake goods!

10:59.770 --> 11:02.180
We're going to burn them!

11:02.700 --> 11:05.670
We'll burn down your stall!

11:06.840 --> 11:07.770
Stop beating me!

11:09.180 --> 11:10.740
Excuse me, excuse me!

11:10.760 --> 11:11.680
Don't fight!

11:12.250 --> 11:13.120
Stop fighting!

11:15.500 --> 11:16.360
Stop fighting!

11:16.410 --> 11:18.320
We know each other!

11:18.390 --> 11:19.550
Alright! Alright!

11:19.600 --> 11:20.980
Don't fight.

11:21.000 --> 11:22.250
-We know each other.
-What happened?

11:22.250 --> 11:23.050
Don't fight.

11:23.960 --> 11:24.620
They bought a batch of shoes

11:24.620 --> 11:25.890
from me to resell.

11:26.030 --> 11:27.520
Some people bought them,
and they wore out quickly,

11:27.520 --> 11:29.380
so they came back demanding I pay.

11:31.650 --> 11:32.130
Look.

11:32.890 --> 11:34.820
These shoes are all like this.

11:35.080 --> 11:36.080
They didn't even last a week.

11:36.080 --> 11:37.240
They're all garbage.

11:37.240 --> 11:38.570
He has two choices now.

11:38.670 --> 11:40.500
First, pay up;

11:40.720 --> 11:42.100
second, burn them all.

11:43.340 --> 11:44.670
Then pay for what you owe

11:44.750 --> 11:46.290
and exchange the goods for new ones.

11:46.290 --> 11:47.440
He wants me to pay 10 times.

11:47.440 --> 11:48.820
How could I have that much money?

11:48.820 --> 11:49.340
I've already sent all my money

11:49.340 --> 11:50.450
to my wife and kid.

11:50.550 --> 11:51.670
I don't have cash here.

11:51.670 --> 11:52.270
If you knew it would be like this,

11:52.270 --> 11:53.370
why did you sell that junk?

11:53.370 --> 11:54.250
Don't mind him. It serves him right.

11:54.250 --> 11:54.720
Let's go.

11:54.720 --> 11:56.050
-I didn't know he would come to me.
-Let's go.

11:56.050 --> 11:56.830
Burn them.

11:57.010 --> 11:58.480
Everything you Chinese sell

11:58.480 --> 11:59.660
is garbage!

12:01.130 --> 12:02.060
What did you say?

12:02.480 --> 12:03.210
Don't fight!

12:03.220 --> 12:05.010
We have goods.

12:05.220 --> 12:07.220
I have goods. I'll swap them for you.

12:07.390 --> 12:08.050
I'll do it.

12:08.910 --> 12:10.640
Chinese goods are all garbage.

12:10.770 --> 12:12.570
What are you going to trade with?

12:12.840 --> 12:13.460
Our shoes

12:13.460 --> 12:14.430
are not like his.

12:14.910 --> 12:16.250
Then let me take a look.

12:18.360 --> 12:19.510
You should have at least
discussed this with me.

12:19.510 --> 12:20.320
Seriously.

12:20.600 --> 12:21.440
Our goods are good.

12:21.440 --> 12:22.650
Come on, look.

12:27.940 --> 12:28.890
His shoes are so bad,

12:28.890 --> 12:30.010
even we wouldn't wear them.

12:30.010 --> 12:30.980
They don't represent Chinese goods.

12:30.980 --> 12:32.200
Our shoes are good.

12:32.550 --> 12:33.750
They can withstand pulling, dragging,

12:33.750 --> 12:35.080
kicking, and stomping.

12:35.410 --> 12:37.510
This is real Chinese quality.

12:41.050 --> 12:41.780
How about it?

12:41.940 --> 12:42.510
Can we swap?

12:42.510 --> 12:43.480
Okay, we can.

12:43.540 --> 12:44.370
We need to check the goods.

12:44.370 --> 12:46.320
Just your three pairs?

12:46.970 --> 12:48.300
How many pairs in total?

12:49.510 --> 12:50.380
Fifty.

12:52.320 --> 12:54.050
Look at the mess you got us into.

12:55.080 --> 12:55.860
Well...

12:55.890 --> 12:57.080
I don't have 50 pairs here.

12:57.080 --> 12:57.790
I have more in my car.

12:57.790 --> 12:58.640
Follow me.

12:59.320 --> 13:00.720
You can go there and pick.

13:02.300 --> 13:04.620
Come with me.

13:04.680 --> 13:05.730
Excuse me.

13:06.280 --> 13:07.090
This way.

13:07.480 --> 13:09.560
Come on. Follow me.

13:10.550 --> 13:11.500
Do as you see fit.

13:11.630 --> 13:12.190
Sir...

13:12.620 --> 13:13.250
Thanks.

13:13.530 --> 13:14.100
Sir,

13:14.140 --> 13:16.870
I will definitely return
the money for the shoes.

13:18.200 --> 13:19.330
I'm not helping you.

13:20.100 --> 13:20.980
I'm doing it to maintain

13:20.980 --> 13:22.910
the reputation of Chinese people.

13:24.220 --> 13:25.500
I know it's bad to sell fakes.

13:25.500 --> 13:26.560
Right? I was wrong.

13:26.840 --> 13:28.320
Your goods are of good quality,

13:28.320 --> 13:29.520
but the profit is low.

13:29.840 --> 13:31.010
How can we make money?

13:31.010 --> 13:32.610
When you do business abroad,

13:32.650 --> 13:34.250
you can't just think about money.

13:34.250 --> 13:35.890
You represent the Chinese people.

13:35.890 --> 13:37.690
Don't lose face for the Chinese.

13:39.650 --> 13:40.890
Sir! Sir! Sir!

13:44.650 --> 13:45.200
Sir,

13:45.510 --> 13:47.040
do you still have the shoes?

13:49.100 --> 13:50.560
I want to restock from you.

13:51.240 --> 13:52.210
From today on,

13:52.510 --> 13:53.970
I will turn over a new leaf.

13:56.870 --> 13:57.290
Okay.

13:58.630 --> 13:59.650
Burn that batch

13:59.650 --> 14:01.120
of terrible shoes of yours first.

14:01.120 --> 14:03.050
I'll burn them. I'll burn them all!

14:03.080 --> 14:04.210
I'll do it right now!

14:04.550 --> 14:05.550
Thanks to Sophia,

14:06.130 --> 14:06.700
we were able

14:06.700 --> 14:08.360
to open up the Russian market.

14:08.720 --> 14:09.650
But to be honest,

14:09.820 --> 14:10.890
I feel

14:10.960 --> 14:11.870
a bit unfulfilled.

14:11.870 --> 14:13.580
Such a good product,

14:13.980 --> 14:15.050
yet we can't openly say

14:15.050 --> 14:16.310
they're made in China.

14:16.750 --> 14:17.340
We have to

14:17.340 --> 14:18.240
sell it abroad

14:18.240 --> 14:19.650
in our Russian friend's name.

14:19.650 --> 14:20.250
When will

14:20.250 --> 14:21.130
everyone know

14:21.130 --> 14:22.030
our Chinese products

14:22.030 --> 14:23.230
are truly excellent?

14:24.240 --> 14:25.620
This is great love.

14:26.050 --> 14:27.850
It's a long and arduous journey.

14:27.940 --> 14:29.000
But it's a good thing.

14:29.000 --> 14:30.170
At least it taught those profiteers

14:30.170 --> 14:31.620
a lesson, right?

14:34.360 --> 14:35.150
Sophia is back.

14:35.150 --> 14:36.210
Time to eat, right?

14:37.620 --> 14:38.670
Well...

14:41.340 --> 14:42.890
Should we bring out the hot dishes first?

14:42.890 --> 14:43.870
Please, this way.

14:43.870 --> 14:44.540
Okay, okay.

14:44.720 --> 14:47.150
Jun, they are from
Wenzhou Hometown Association.

14:47.150 --> 14:48.080
Nice to meet you.

14:48.870 --> 14:49.700
Nice to meet you.

14:49.700 --> 14:50.070
Hello.

14:50.070 --> 14:51.320
-Hello.
-Hello. Hello.

14:51.320 --> 14:52.820
We are representatives

14:52.860 --> 14:54.870
of the Wenzhou Hometown Association
in Russia.

14:54.870 --> 14:56.030
We heard you were here,

14:56.030 --> 14:57.170
so we hurried over to visit.

14:57.170 --> 14:57.700
Thank you.

14:57.700 --> 14:58.500
-Okay.
-Well…

14:59.290 --> 15:00.240
Did you come

15:00.250 --> 15:01.710
to visit us for something?

15:01.720 --> 15:03.720
Thanks to your being there that day,

15:04.630 --> 15:07.430
the reputation of Chinese businessmen
was saved.

15:09.000 --> 15:09.620
So,

15:10.000 --> 15:11.320
our Wenzhou Chamber of Commerce

15:11.320 --> 15:13.320
made a pennant for you.

15:13.790 --> 15:15.720
This is a token of our respect.

15:16.290 --> 15:18.290
We hope you keep up the good work.

15:18.600 --> 15:19.940
Please accept it.

15:23.150 --> 15:24.700
Here, accept it.

15:25.750 --> 15:27.430
This... This is

15:27.580 --> 15:29.130
an affirmation from our compatriots.

15:29.130 --> 15:30.220
This is an unexpected harvest.

15:30.220 --> 15:31.080
You deserve it.

15:31.290 --> 15:33.100
You are role models
for Chinese businessmen,

15:33.100 --> 15:35.030
always putting credibility first

15:35.320 --> 15:36.790
and giving priority to quality.

15:36.790 --> 15:37.590
-Yes.
-Right?

15:37.820 --> 15:38.960
Well...

15:39.200 --> 15:40.670
Thank you for the affirmation.

15:40.670 --> 15:41.670
I will definitely

15:41.790 --> 15:42.860
hang it at home.

15:43.460 --> 15:44.770
Let's take a picture.

15:44.790 --> 15:45.670
Sure.

15:45.670 --> 15:46.170
Please.

15:46.190 --> 15:46.830
Please stand in the middle.

15:46.570 --> 15:50.300
[Outstanding Merchant—
Bringing Honor to the Nation]

15:49.010 --> 15:50.000
Get a little closer.

15:50.000 --> 15:50.870
Okay.

15:50.870 --> 15:52.750
Okay, raise the pennant
a little higher on this side.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.100
Okay.

15:53.580 --> 15:55.290
President, look at the camera.

15:55.290 --> 15:56.860
Three, two, one.

15:58.460 --> 15:59.240
Alright.

15:59.270 --> 16:00.340
Thank you.

16:01.750 --> 16:04.580
You are the president
of Wenzhou Hometown Association?

16:04.580 --> 16:06.250
Our factory is also in Wenzhou.

16:06.250 --> 16:06.770
Right.

16:06.910 --> 16:08.530
President, what happened that day

16:08.530 --> 16:09.930
was just a coincidence.

16:10.200 --> 16:12.000
Although the problem has been solved,

16:12.000 --> 16:13.220
a pennant

16:13.250 --> 16:14.670
can't change the Russians'

16:14.670 --> 16:16.630
overall impression of Chinese goods.

16:16.630 --> 16:18.030
We are here doing business

16:18.030 --> 16:19.630
not just for a one-time deal.

16:19.660 --> 16:20.740
We want Russians,

16:20.760 --> 16:21.760
when they think of Chinese goods,

16:21.760 --> 16:23.340
to think of them as reliable.

16:23.340 --> 16:25.980
We want them to say that Chinese products
are of high quality.

16:25.980 --> 16:26.960
Someone has to take the lead.

16:26.960 --> 16:27.430
Yes.

16:27.650 --> 16:29.250
Someone has to take the lead.

16:29.510 --> 16:30.580
We know this.

16:30.790 --> 16:32.500
These fake and shoddy products

16:32.500 --> 16:33.150
have made us

16:33.150 --> 16:34.550
legitimate businessmen

16:34.580 --> 16:35.840
suffer.

16:37.150 --> 16:38.010
How about this?

16:38.740 --> 16:39.980
Print a few more copies

16:39.980 --> 16:41.360
of the photo we just took for us.

16:41.360 --> 16:42.600
We'll post them at home.

16:42.600 --> 16:43.000
Right.

16:43.000 --> 16:43.890
And in our factory.

16:43.890 --> 16:44.960
And let's make more

16:44.980 --> 16:45.920
of this pennant.

16:46.250 --> 16:46.970
Later,

16:47.360 --> 16:48.220
you can take them back

16:48.220 --> 16:49.830
and hang them in front of the shops

16:49.830 --> 16:50.980
that sell genuine goods.

16:50.980 --> 16:52.720
Hang them wherever they are conspicuous.

16:52.720 --> 16:53.870
First, this can serve as

16:53.870 --> 16:55.080
a reminder

16:55.170 --> 16:56.080
to those opportunists.

16:56.080 --> 16:56.830
Second,

16:57.030 --> 16:57.790
it will give us—

16:57.790 --> 16:59.120
those who want to do legitimate business—

16:59.120 --> 17:00.120
more confidence.

17:00.340 --> 17:01.030
Okay.

17:01.280 --> 17:03.310
Okay, I'll handle this.

17:05.810 --> 17:06.250
In the blink of an eye,

17:06.250 --> 17:08.069
Shengli is leaving tomorrow.

17:08.810 --> 17:10.270
I really hate to see him go.

17:10.829 --> 17:12.290
But there's nothing I can do.

17:12.290 --> 17:13.940
His sweetheart is far away,

17:13.940 --> 17:14.869
waiting for him.

17:19.050 --> 17:20.380
I want to say something.

17:23.750 --> 17:26.240
Thank you so much for bringing me along

17:26.260 --> 17:27.390
to do this business.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.930
It made me very happy.

17:30.740 --> 17:32.810
Leave the business here to me.

17:32.920 --> 17:34.320
I'll take good care of it.

17:34.440 --> 17:35.680
I hope Shengli

17:35.830 --> 17:38.040
will visit my home often.

17:39.850 --> 17:40.380
Sophia.

17:41.810 --> 17:43.160
I look forward to your visit to Beijing.

17:43.160 --> 17:43.960
We'll take you

17:44.000 --> 17:45.420
to eat Beijing local food

17:45.900 --> 17:48.200
and to the Great Wall
and the Forbidden City.

17:48.200 --> 17:48.690
Okay.

17:49.010 --> 17:51.140
Going to Beijing is my dream.

17:51.200 --> 17:51.810
Cheers!

17:52.200 --> 17:53.930
Come on, let's toast together.

17:53.940 --> 17:54.440
In China,

17:54.440 --> 17:56.400
I'll take you wherever you want to go.

17:56.400 --> 17:56.810
Okay.

18:01.790 --> 18:02.660
This business

18:03.690 --> 18:05.610
just somehow worked out.

18:06.200 --> 18:08.020
No, I was confused.

18:08.420 --> 18:09.870
You had everything under control.

18:09.870 --> 18:11.220
What are you talking about?

18:11.220 --> 18:12.200
Jun, if you weren't here,

18:12.200 --> 18:13.330
could I have done it?

18:15.880 --> 18:16.810
You can tell right away

18:16.810 --> 18:18.470
that you're good at business.

18:18.810 --> 18:19.500
Ordinary people

18:19.500 --> 18:20.920
don't usually catch my eye.

18:20.920 --> 18:21.790
But Shengli,

18:22.510 --> 18:23.070
after working together,

18:23.070 --> 18:24.420
I really admire you.

18:26.090 --> 18:27.910
So I'm not bad, huh?

18:28.480 --> 18:29.570
Not bad. Very good.

18:33.880 --> 18:35.570
I was running back and forth recently

18:35.570 --> 18:37.880
and had no time to think about this.

18:38.640 --> 18:39.680
Lately,

18:39.770 --> 18:41.400
things have stabilized a bit.

18:41.400 --> 18:43.260
The debts are almost paid off too.

18:43.440 --> 18:45.610
Actually, I've really thought about it.

18:45.610 --> 18:46.310
Maybe...

18:48.030 --> 18:49.760
this is really what I should do.

18:50.530 --> 18:52.140
Let's fix

18:52.140 --> 18:53.540
this model in the future.

18:53.640 --> 18:55.040
I'll be in charge of sales

18:55.070 --> 18:56.220
and business negotiations.

18:56.220 --> 18:58.000
Jun, you'll take charge of local matters.

18:58.000 --> 18:59.770
And we can take those...

19:00.270 --> 19:01.230
Zhuang Zhuang.

19:02.070 --> 19:04.310
Production is our pillar.

19:04.810 --> 19:06.470
Zhuang Zhuang is your pillar.

19:08.700 --> 19:09.330
Yes.

19:12.400 --> 19:13.500
There was one time

19:13.500 --> 19:14.700
when I came to Russia,

19:15.660 --> 19:17.510
my mom made a long-distance call,

19:17.510 --> 19:20.310
insisting that I go back
and eat zhajiang noodles.

19:20.700 --> 19:22.030
I said, "You called from so far away

19:22.030 --> 19:23.530
just to tell me
to go back for Zhajiang noodles?"

19:23.530 --> 19:25.130
I told her I was making money.

19:25.380 --> 19:26.510
My mom said, "You?

19:26.510 --> 19:27.910
Can you even make money?"

19:32.830 --> 19:33.760
Later I realized

19:36.290 --> 19:37.750
that my mom just missed me.

19:38.380 --> 19:40.640
That was the last time I talked to my mom.

19:42.170 --> 19:43.530
If my mom could see now

19:43.530 --> 19:44.730
that I can make money,

19:45.640 --> 19:47.170
wouldn't she be very happy?

19:48.180 --> 19:49.310
She would.

19:49.310 --> 19:50.710
She definitely would be.

19:51.660 --> 19:53.530
Jun. When we get back,

19:53.530 --> 19:54.900
I'll treat you to Zhajiang noodles.

19:54.900 --> 19:56.270
I'll treat you every day.

19:56.270 --> 19:58.010
No, let Liangliang do it.

19:58.800 --> 20:00.880
Let Liangliang make Zhajiang noodles
for me.

20:00.880 --> 20:02.180
By then, I'll throw money in his face

20:02.180 --> 20:02.460
and make him

20:02.460 --> 20:03.900
make Zhajiang noodles for me all night.

20:03.900 --> 20:05.500
I'll throw it in his face too.

20:09.310 --> 20:11.090
Come on, let's have a drink.

20:11.590 --> 20:12.050
Come on.

20:22.880 --> 20:29.590
The garden is quiet late at night.

20:30.510 --> 20:35.550
Only the wind is singing softly.

20:36.140 --> 20:40.200
How beautiful the night is.

20:40.310 --> 20:43.920
It captivates my heart—

20:44.420 --> 20:49.960
the night in the suburbs of Moscow.

20:50.570 --> 20:54.200
How beautiful the night is.

20:54.680 --> 20:57.900
It captivates my heart—

20:58.440 --> 21:03.570
the night in the suburbs of Moscow.

21:14.500 --> 21:16.800
Help me check your bag

21:17.000 --> 21:19.000
and see if the things
we're bringing for your mom

21:19.000 --> 21:19.790
are all there.

21:19.790 --> 21:21.850
Make sure we didn't forget anything.

21:21.920 --> 21:22.380
Okay.

21:41.200 --> 21:42.130
You bought this?

21:42.980 --> 21:43.780
Do you like it?

21:52.420 --> 21:53.370
Open it and see.

22:04.810 --> 22:07.010
Tao Liangliang, Shen Ranran.

22:05.850 --> 22:08.090
[Tao Liangliang] [Shen Ranran]

22:07.810 --> 22:09.140
I am your shell,

22:10.720 --> 22:12.050
always protecting you.

22:19.310 --> 22:20.630
[Shen Ranran]

22:19.640 --> 22:20.700
There's more?

22:22.830 --> 22:24.310
Why doesn't this one have a name?

22:24.310 --> 22:25.940
This is our child.

22:27.480 --> 22:28.620
You can name it.

22:29.050 --> 22:30.850
What should we call it? Tao what?

22:31.700 --> 22:32.400
Tao Ranran.

22:32.750 --> 22:33.940
Tao Ranran?

22:34.160 --> 22:35.570
Okay, good name.

22:36.440 --> 22:37.660
There's a green one too?

22:37.660 --> 22:39.380
This is our second child.

22:42.830 --> 22:44.360
How many are there in total?

22:44.440 --> 22:45.770
This is our third child.

22:46.900 --> 22:47.680
One more?

22:49.240 --> 22:50.300
This is our fourth.

22:50.420 --> 22:52.050
Didn't our parents' generation

22:52.050 --> 22:54.730
all have many children?

22:54.880 --> 22:55.960
There's more?

22:56.070 --> 22:56.610
Yeah.

22:59.200 --> 23:01.850
How many do you want me to have?

23:16.110 --> 23:17.370
You bought this for me?

23:17.960 --> 23:19.510
When I proposed before,

23:21.530 --> 23:22.460
I promised you

23:23.850 --> 23:25.180
I would make it up to you.

23:27.220 --> 23:28.220
What about yours?

23:29.240 --> 23:30.290
Mine...

23:31.250 --> 23:31.880
faded,

23:33.000 --> 23:34.000
so I threw it away.

23:38.050 --> 23:41.250
Liangliang, do you think...

23:43.000 --> 23:43.900
we will really

23:43.900 --> 23:45.310
be blessed by everyone?

23:50.660 --> 23:52.420
We didn't come into this world

23:54.200 --> 23:55.480
for no reason.

23:59.400 --> 24:00.570
After we met—

24:01.160 --> 24:02.960
and in all the tomorrows to come—

24:04.590 --> 24:05.990
let's rely on each other.

24:09.720 --> 24:10.200
Okay.

24:12.180 --> 24:12.660
Okay.

24:13.750 --> 24:14.850
Quick, put it on me.

24:34.000 --> 24:35.000
Hello, Mrs. Shen.

24:35.380 --> 24:36.640
My name is Tao Liangliang.

24:36.640 --> 24:37.640
I'm from Beijing.

24:39.880 --> 24:40.510
These are some

24:40.510 --> 24:42.180
local specialties from Beijing.

24:42.180 --> 24:43.710
I don't know your taste.

24:44.200 --> 24:46.220
If you like any of them,

24:46.500 --> 24:48.510
I will bring you more next time.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.080
And this.

24:49.270 --> 24:50.790
This is braised pork knuckle
that I asked my dad

24:50.790 --> 24:51.830
to make specially for you.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.160
I've vacuum-sealed it.

25:00.980 --> 25:01.970
These

25:02.200 --> 25:03.790
aren't to my taste.

25:09.550 --> 25:10.220
Mom.

25:15.900 --> 25:18.160
Is there... anything you want to tell me?

25:19.220 --> 25:19.890
Mrs. Shen.

25:20.110 --> 25:21.160
We came here today

25:22.530 --> 25:24.240
to talk about us.

25:25.570 --> 25:26.810
About you two?

25:27.140 --> 25:28.200
What is it?

25:32.610 --> 25:33.790
Well, my grandpa

25:33.790 --> 25:35.190
left behind an old house.

25:35.900 --> 25:36.940
Then

25:37.380 --> 25:38.940
my parents renovated it

25:39.110 --> 25:40.640
and opened a small restaurant.

25:40.640 --> 25:42.640
Lately, they've been talking about

25:42.640 --> 25:44.070
remodeling the back area.

25:44.070 --> 25:46.380
They plan to live in the restaurant
in the future.

25:46.380 --> 25:48.000
And they'll leave the house

25:48.770 --> 25:50.300
they're living in now to us.

25:52.220 --> 25:54.280
For us to live in after we get married.

26:00.610 --> 26:01.210
This is...

26:01.610 --> 26:02.860
too ridiculous.

26:05.350 --> 26:06.610
After you get married?

26:07.640 --> 26:08.480
Ranran,

26:08.790 --> 26:10.190
you are getting married?

26:12.010 --> 26:13.870
How can you afford to get married?

26:14.810 --> 26:16.110
Neither of you

26:16.640 --> 26:18.880
has a proper job.

26:19.010 --> 26:21.400
Where will you get the money to marry?

26:22.180 --> 26:23.050
How will you support a family?

26:23.050 --> 26:24.780
How will you raise children?

26:25.160 --> 26:26.180
Will you keep asking your parents

26:26.180 --> 26:27.510
for money in the future?

26:28.420 --> 26:28.900
Mom.

26:30.460 --> 26:31.880
We have jobs.

26:33.010 --> 26:33.870
Liangliang...

26:34.010 --> 26:35.290
Liangliang is very good at

26:35.290 --> 26:36.620
playing the saxophone.

26:36.640 --> 26:38.310
Many people hire him to perform.

26:38.310 --> 26:39.910
He makes thousands per show.

26:40.030 --> 26:41.290
He also does business.

26:41.720 --> 26:44.120
He goes to Russia for international trade.

26:44.140 --> 26:44.920
A single trip

26:44.920 --> 26:47.050
can earn him tens of thousands of yuan.

26:47.070 --> 26:49.570
In the future... the two of us...

26:50.790 --> 26:52.120
will work hard together

26:53.010 --> 26:54.070
and earn more money

26:54.720 --> 26:56.430
to support you.

26:56.960 --> 26:57.350
Mrs. Shen,

26:57.350 --> 26:59.050
I will treat Ranran well.

27:01.030 --> 27:01.960
I will work hard.

27:03.070 --> 27:04.290
You will work hard?

27:04.940 --> 27:06.030
You are at this age

27:06.030 --> 27:08.030
and you haven't achieved anything.

27:08.300 --> 27:09.740
And you want to get married?

27:09.740 --> 27:11.050
Stop talking big.

27:11.880 --> 27:13.260
Anyway, let me tell you,

27:13.750 --> 27:14.570
I won't agree

27:15.240 --> 27:16.250
to your marriage.

27:18.900 --> 27:19.830
And Ranran,

27:19.960 --> 27:22.000
if you want to be with this poor boy,

27:22.720 --> 27:23.540
just do it.

27:24.720 --> 27:25.720
In the future,

27:25.880 --> 27:27.140
don't come to me again.

27:29.980 --> 27:31.570
I will never agree!

27:44.740 --> 27:45.320
Let's go.

27:46.200 --> 27:47.600
Let's go back to Beijing.

27:51.180 --> 27:53.140
You've bought everything you need.

27:53.140 --> 27:54.920
See if there's anything else
you want to take back.

27:54.920 --> 27:56.330
We still have some time
before the train leaves.

27:56.330 --> 27:57.660
That's enough.

27:57.930 --> 27:59.260
When are you going back?

28:01.200 --> 28:02.670
I am so busy here.

28:02.790 --> 28:04.270
I have to cooperate with you here

28:04.270 --> 28:05.200
and support you.

28:06.420 --> 28:07.150
That's true.

28:07.530 --> 28:09.730
And you can spend more time with Sophia.

28:09.830 --> 28:10.810
Why are you always joking?

28:10.810 --> 28:12.220
Stop joking.

28:12.250 --> 28:13.680
I have to do business here

28:13.700 --> 28:14.380
and cooperate with you.

28:14.380 --> 28:15.580
I need to support you.

28:15.750 --> 28:16.150
Right?

28:16.250 --> 28:16.920
Besides,

28:17.480 --> 28:18.550
Sophia and I...

28:20.000 --> 28:21.060
Is it that obvious?

28:22.610 --> 28:23.870
What are brothers for?

28:24.700 --> 28:25.590
I can tell what you're thinking

28:25.590 --> 28:27.110
without you saying a word.

28:32.450 --> 28:33.920
Do you think she'll like me?

28:33.920 --> 28:34.980
I can't really say.

28:36.220 --> 28:36.680
Yeah.

28:37.380 --> 28:38.240
I'm not young anymore.

28:38.240 --> 28:39.180
She's quite tall

28:39.480 --> 28:40.350
and better-looking than me.

28:40.350 --> 28:42.080
Then why did she help us so much?

28:43.290 --> 28:44.350
What does she want?

28:44.980 --> 28:45.440
Come on.

28:45.940 --> 28:47.110
You know,

28:47.240 --> 28:49.170
you're decisive in other matters.

28:49.240 --> 28:51.100
Why are you so hesitant with this?

28:56.060 --> 28:57.190
Me? Hesitant?

28:57.850 --> 28:59.780
It's because I didn't get a chance.

29:00.010 --> 29:01.740
If you give me a chance, I'll...

29:04.330 --> 29:04.990
Wait here.

29:09.810 --> 29:11.850
Flowers! Flowers!

29:13.000 --> 29:20.700
Flowers! Flowers!

29:24.680 --> 29:25.660
Kid, come here.

29:27.640 --> 29:29.370
Flowers, sir?

29:29.570 --> 29:31.300
Which flower represents love?

29:31.420 --> 29:31.950
This one.

29:32.240 --> 29:33.940
No red roses?

29:35.090 --> 29:36.820
You don't understand Chinese?

29:37.810 --> 29:38.380
Learn more Chinese,

29:38.380 --> 29:39.880
and you'll make a fortune in the future.

29:39.880 --> 29:40.610
Thank you.

29:40.610 --> 29:41.960
Thanks. Give me the change.

29:41.960 --> 29:42.960
Thank you.

29:43.200 --> 29:43.940
You don't understand this?

29:43.940 --> 29:45.750
Do you understand "give me the change"?

29:45.750 --> 29:46.110
Sir,

29:46.110 --> 29:47.350
please buy our flowers.

29:47.350 --> 29:49.040
So we'll be able to go home.

29:49.380 --> 29:50.510
I don't understand.

29:51.140 --> 29:52.090
Hurry up and go home.

29:52.090 --> 29:53.760
One bouquet is enough for me.

29:54.270 --> 29:54.920
I'll give you some money.

29:54.920 --> 29:56.010
Take it as pocket money.

29:56.010 --> 29:57.020
Study hard.

30:04.090 --> 30:05.150
What are you doing?

30:05.770 --> 30:06.830
What are you doing?

31:05.940 --> 31:06.970
The attackers...

31:13.180 --> 31:15.110
The attackers have been caught.

31:15.980 --> 31:17.240
They're Sergey's men.

31:19.200 --> 31:21.360
After the cremation ceremony tomorrow,

31:20.430 --> 31:26.220
[Death Certificate]

31:24.400 --> 31:25.810
you can take him home.

31:29.920 --> 31:31.420
He always liked to sit here

31:31.460 --> 31:32.610
and joke with us.

31:34.480 --> 31:35.420
This fool.

32:16.620 --> 32:20.220
♪ In one cold night of one year,
a dream took root ♪

32:22.330 --> 32:26.060
♪ One vow still holds a trace of warmth ♪

32:28.160 --> 32:32.740
♪ By one window, we once
sat together under a gentle light ♪

32:33.710 --> 32:38.300
♪ Yet in one turning,
we missed half a lifetime ♪

32:35.570 --> 32:36.650
-Jun.
-Jun.

32:36.670 --> 32:37.380
You flatter me.

32:37.380 --> 32:38.510
That's all in the past.

32:38.510 --> 32:39.830
Now I mainly do business.

32:39.830 --> 32:43.700
♪ One beam of light
scattered into the stars ♪

32:43.740 --> 32:45.480
The four of us will work together as one,

32:45.480 --> 32:46.920
charge forward, and make money!

32:46.180 --> 32:49.470
♪ In some emptiness,
I learned to be whole ♪

32:47.000 --> 32:48.510
We will make a fortune!

32:48.720 --> 32:50.460
I have to keep you safe.

32:50.570 --> 32:52.610
We made it here safely.

32:51.750 --> 32:56.520
♪ At one station,
the sound of farewell became forever ♪

32:52.700 --> 32:54.400
We must leave in one piece too.

32:54.420 --> 32:55.590
Be careful in everything you do.

32:55.590 --> 32:56.480
You have to listen to me.

32:56.480 --> 32:57.510
Do you understand?

32:57.510 --> 33:02.110
♪ Some journey has no way back ♪

33:01.110 --> 33:02.350
I still hadn't figured out

33:02.350 --> 33:03.950
what kind of person you were.

33:04.140 --> 33:05.770
Now you know what kind of person I am?

33:05.770 --> 33:07.220
You have many good qualities.

33:05.920 --> 33:10.380
♪ In one winter,
my hands were no longer cold ♪

33:07.810 --> 33:09.670
Just as many as the bad ones I have.

33:10.510 --> 33:11.460
Trust Lucky Ma,

33:11.340 --> 33:16.410
♪ My path ahead is carved into
every line of my palms ♪

33:11.460 --> 33:13.570
work with Lucky Ma,
and good luck will find you!

33:13.570 --> 33:15.180
We're actually very suited
for doing business.

33:15.180 --> 33:16.740
Look, you have a strong physique,

33:16.740 --> 33:17.660
and I have a smart brain.

33:17.550 --> 33:22.250
♪ One spring,
I opened the envelope of the past ♪

33:17.680 --> 33:18.880
Let's shout a slogan.

33:18.880 --> 33:19.720
It's called,

33:19.720 --> 33:20.810
"Life is about striving."

33:20.810 --> 33:21.140
I'll shout 'life'.

33:21.140 --> 33:21.680
And you shout "is about striving."

33:21.680 --> 33:22.290
-Okay.
-Okay!

33:22.290 --> 33:22.980
Life!

33:22.980 --> 33:25.160
Is about striving!

33:23.230 --> 33:30.930
♪ The answers were already
written on every page of life ♪

33:37.940 --> 33:39.290
If you walk out today,

33:40.140 --> 33:41.970
we're done!

33:42.030 --> 33:43.030
Fine, we're done.

33:45.060 --> 33:47.990
Even if you die out there,
it has nothing to do with me!

33:52.310 --> 33:53.720
You invested more and earned more,

33:53.720 --> 33:55.010
and you can buy a car later.

33:55.010 --> 33:56.220
You invested little and earned little,

33:55.830 --> 33:58.720
♪ Enduring forever ♪

33:56.540 --> 33:58.270
I still gave you a higher total.

34:14.960 --> 34:16.889
Is everything about Jun arranged?

34:24.780 --> 34:25.440
Recently,

34:25.460 --> 34:28.320
Liangliang has been
keeping Jun's father company.

34:31.190 --> 34:32.090
The place

34:32.090 --> 34:33.440
we chose for Jun...

34:35.300 --> 34:36.400
is quite spacious.

34:37.320 --> 34:38.850
He will definitely like it.

34:45.210 --> 34:46.440
Last time we came here,

34:46.440 --> 34:48.100
we were talking about movies.

34:50.070 --> 34:52.000
It seems that in the blink of an eye,

34:52.340 --> 34:54.350
our lives

34:55.530 --> 34:56.460
have

34:58.700 --> 34:59.580
taken a turn

34:59.610 --> 35:00.670
we never imagined.

35:02.570 --> 35:03.370
It's like life

35:03.400 --> 35:05.110
was suddenly put on pause,

35:06.150 --> 35:07.560
forcing us to stop

35:07.590 --> 35:09.790
and think carefully about many things.

35:11.810 --> 35:13.120
While my mom was sick,

35:13.150 --> 35:14.350
I did a lot of thinking

35:14.980 --> 35:16.580
and gave up the competition.

35:22.960 --> 35:23.840
Lately,

35:25.140 --> 35:27.280
I often think about

35:27.850 --> 35:28.370
the days

35:28.400 --> 35:30.200
we chased our dreams in Beijing.

35:30.760 --> 35:32.180
We laughed, and we cried.

35:33.550 --> 35:35.280
Every face was so bright.

35:38.860 --> 35:39.670
Sometimes

35:39.690 --> 35:41.620
we did run into some difficulties,

35:41.650 --> 35:43.110
but being together

35:43.940 --> 35:44.530
made it

35:44.550 --> 35:45.800
not feel so bad.

35:51.280 --> 35:52.140
Thank you.

35:52.960 --> 35:55.220
For bringing me to Seasons Change Hostel

35:55.360 --> 35:56.190
and letting me feel

35:56.190 --> 35:57.110
so much warmth.

35:58.260 --> 36:00.060
I should be the one thanking you.

36:01.090 --> 36:02.960
You gave me a lot of warmth.

36:09.250 --> 36:10.250
I'm done singing.

36:15.510 --> 36:17.260
Singing does make me happy,

36:18.080 --> 36:19.350
but I've realized

36:20.150 --> 36:21.750
that passion and profession

36:22.360 --> 36:23.620
can't always coexist.

36:26.000 --> 36:27.610
Sometimes, chasing too hard

36:29.070 --> 36:29.980
can actually drain

36:29.980 --> 36:30.910
your love for it.

36:34.690 --> 36:36.010
So now I want to try

36:36.030 --> 36:37.970
designing clothes.

36:38.230 --> 36:39.370
Back at Ruhua,

36:39.900 --> 36:41.720
I found I actually

36:41.780 --> 36:42.980
quite like it.

36:44.730 --> 36:45.790
I'll give it a shot.

36:46.190 --> 36:47.990
Maybe this path suits me better.

36:49.800 --> 36:50.840
You are right.

36:52.550 --> 36:55.070
Few people manage to turn their passion

36:55.090 --> 36:56.190
into a career.

36:57.030 --> 36:58.690
I've also thought it through.

36:59.440 --> 37:02.300
Writing is still my passion.

37:03.650 --> 37:05.390
So I'll just keep it

37:05.610 --> 37:07.720
as something that's always ongoing.

37:09.570 --> 37:11.460
During my time in Russia,

37:12.360 --> 37:13.400
I thought a lot.

37:15.260 --> 37:17.390
I realized that doing business

37:19.620 --> 37:21.680
also brings me a lot of satisfaction.

37:22.280 --> 37:23.470
Didn't you just say

37:23.500 --> 37:24.960
you want to try designing?

37:25.590 --> 37:28.120
Then I'll help you
to sell your clothes later.

37:30.900 --> 37:33.290
Maybe our previous dreams

37:34.760 --> 37:36.160
just lacked a bit of luck.

37:36.530 --> 37:37.790
But it doesn't matter.

37:38.610 --> 37:39.800
Now we can say

37:39.800 --> 37:41.060
we have a shared dream.

37:43.340 --> 37:44.090
I used to think

37:44.090 --> 37:45.900
dreams were the most important thing.

37:45.900 --> 37:46.920
But now I feel

37:47.980 --> 37:50.180
the person who can chase dreams with you

37:50.710 --> 37:51.970
is the most important.

38:02.630 --> 38:03.860
No matter which path

38:05.110 --> 38:06.640
life takes us in the future,

38:10.360 --> 38:11.000
I hope I can

38:11.010 --> 38:12.190
hold your hand

38:15.860 --> 38:17.390
and keep walking together.

38:40.840 --> 38:42.030
Are you really getting married,

38:42.030 --> 38:42.930
Ranran?

38:43.210 --> 38:44.010
Yes.

38:44.030 --> 38:45.000
I'd like to invite you

38:45.000 --> 38:46.550
and your parents to come to the wedding.

38:46.550 --> 38:48.080
I miss you so much.

38:48.340 --> 38:49.470
That's great.

38:49.710 --> 38:50.860
I can live in the Seasons Change Hostel

38:50.860 --> 38:52.330
with everyone again.

38:52.360 --> 38:53.010
Oh, no.

38:53.590 --> 38:54.170
This kid,

38:54.190 --> 38:56.220
you were influenced by Liangliang.

38:56.260 --> 38:57.230
You're just a kid,

38:57.230 --> 38:59.560
and you don't want
to live at home anymore.

38:59.800 --> 39:00.520
Ranran,

39:00.630 --> 39:03.260
your aunt wants to talk to you.

39:03.920 --> 39:04.380
Okay.

39:04.980 --> 39:05.580
Go ahead.

39:07.530 --> 39:08.760
Ranran.

39:09.340 --> 39:11.410
Farming has been busy recently,

39:11.690 --> 39:13.090
so I might not be able

39:13.130 --> 39:15.290
to attend your wedding.

39:15.820 --> 39:17.380
I'll have Xiaobao

39:17.420 --> 39:19.970
bring my gift to you.

39:21.210 --> 39:25.460
I wish you a happy marriage

39:26.300 --> 39:28.710
and a long life together.

39:29.170 --> 39:30.160
Great.

39:30.230 --> 39:31.480
Well said.

39:32.180 --> 39:33.700
Have a baby soon!

39:34.120 --> 39:35.320
Have a baby soon!

39:35.400 --> 39:38.670
Have a baby soon!

39:38.900 --> 39:40.210
Thank you, Mrs. Guo.

39:41.280 --> 39:42.650
When I'm free,

39:42.860 --> 39:43.550
I'll go to Henan specifically

39:43.550 --> 39:44.880
to visit you.

39:46.050 --> 39:47.440
You're welcome.

39:48.090 --> 39:48.730
Okay!

39:49.710 --> 39:51.010
I'll hang up now.

39:54.940 --> 39:56.230
She can speak now?

39:56.900 --> 39:58.810
She said quite a lot.

40:01.760 --> 40:02.710
Everyone at the Seasons Change Hostel

40:02.710 --> 40:03.970
is bringing good news.

40:03.980 --> 40:07.000
Shengli and Zhuang Zhuang
have also returned to Beijing.

40:07.000 --> 40:08.010
I'll go tidy up the room.

40:08.010 --> 40:09.650
Really? I'll go with you.

40:09.760 --> 40:10.650
Let's go then.

40:11.840 --> 40:12.300
Come on.

40:14.820 --> 40:15.980
So beautiful.

40:17.210 --> 40:18.360
You're the most beautiful bride.

40:18.360 --> 40:19.360
This is the most beautiful dress

40:19.360 --> 40:20.620
I have ever worn.

40:20.730 --> 40:21.440
Really?

40:22.650 --> 40:24.150
You've been so busy lately,

40:24.150 --> 40:25.940
yet you still made this outfit for me.

40:25.940 --> 40:27.470
What are you talking about?

40:27.590 --> 40:28.780
For such an important day,

40:28.780 --> 40:30.200
I had to make it for you.

40:35.760 --> 40:36.760
From now on,

40:37.000 --> 40:38.280
I won't be around you,

40:39.230 --> 40:41.050
but you still need to look pretty.

40:41.050 --> 40:42.770
Most importantly, be happy.

40:43.090 --> 40:43.940
Of course.

40:45.190 --> 40:46.440
Zhuang, come with me.

40:49.070 --> 40:49.600
Sit here.

40:54.820 --> 40:55.680
This is for you.

40:56.610 --> 40:57.380
For me?

41:03.150 --> 41:04.440
I was afraid I wouldn't be there

41:04.440 --> 41:05.590
for your important moments,

41:05.590 --> 41:06.510
so I bought this

41:06.550 --> 41:08.940
little golden lock
for your future baby in advance.

41:08.940 --> 41:10.600
You bought this way too early.

41:11.190 --> 41:11.920
No, I didn't.

41:15.570 --> 41:16.340
You

41:16.780 --> 41:18.500
spent all your money on us.

41:19.430 --> 41:20.540
You sound

41:20.570 --> 41:22.090
like a matriarch.

41:23.880 --> 41:24.480
I love it.

41:28.420 --> 41:30.650
You just said
you wouldn't be here anymore?

41:30.650 --> 41:31.780
Where are you going?

41:31.900 --> 41:34.040
Isn't going abroad popular now?

41:34.130 --> 41:35.840
While you were away,

41:36.070 --> 41:37.300
I took foreign language classes

41:37.300 --> 41:38.430
and learned French.

41:38.670 --> 41:39.720
French?

41:40.030 --> 41:41.280
Are you going to France?

41:41.280 --> 41:41.980
Yes.

41:42.280 --> 41:44.010
That's the capital of fashion.

41:44.500 --> 41:45.780
I have a classmate in France

41:45.780 --> 41:48.060
who runs a group tour business

41:48.090 --> 41:50.150
specifically for Chinese tourists.

41:50.300 --> 41:50.590
I think

41:50.590 --> 41:51.710
it's a great opportunity.

41:51.710 --> 41:53.110
And I want to give it a try.

41:53.550 --> 41:55.820
Mr. Guo just paid me back.

41:56.150 --> 41:57.320
And Liangliang's parents

41:57.320 --> 41:58.780
are very supportive of us.

41:58.880 --> 41:59.410
They said

41:59.440 --> 42:00.420
young people should

42:00.420 --> 42:02.150
go out and seek their fortunes.

42:02.210 --> 42:03.630
Once my French is good enough,

42:03.630 --> 42:05.090
we'll go to France.

42:06.070 --> 42:06.870
That's great.

42:07.880 --> 42:09.010
But it's so far away.

42:09.320 --> 42:10.600
Will you two be okay?

42:11.070 --> 42:13.930
We've been through so much together.

42:14.150 --> 42:16.740
We're indestructible warriors.

42:17.670 --> 42:19.860
It's just that French is too hard.

42:21.400 --> 42:22.310
"Hello."

42:22.610 --> 42:24.110
"I'm doing well too."

42:28.380 --> 42:29.360
When you first got here,

42:29.360 --> 42:31.160
you were like a little hedgehog.

42:31.400 --> 42:34.130
Now you're getting married
in the blink of an eye.

42:34.730 --> 42:36.410
Zhuang, why are you crying?

42:36.900 --> 42:37.740
I'll miss you.

42:40.550 --> 42:42.880
For the past 2 years
at the Seasons Change Hostel,

42:42.880 --> 42:43.530
thank you.

42:44.340 --> 42:45.270
No need for that.

42:48.860 --> 42:49.580
Alright.

42:52.440 --> 42:52.920
That's great.
